The,Google,Play,Game,Services,API,allows,developers,to,add,features,such,as,achievements,leaderboards,events,quests,and,multiplayer,support,to,their,web,and,mobile,games,It,can,also,be,used,to,analyze,player,behavior,by,defining,events,and,capturing,metrics,about,those,events,Getting,Started,instructions,are,provided,for,iOS,Android,C,and,web,based,games